ation and execution of new legal documents.<br /><br />\r<b>Change of Sharer (Tenant's Request)</b><br /><br />\r\u00a350 (inc. VAT) per replacement tenant or any reasonable costs incurred if higher.\rTo cover the costs associated with taking landlord's instructions, new tenant\rreferencing and Right-to-Rent checks, deposit registration as well as the preparation\rand execution of new legal documents.<br /><br />\r<b>Early Termination (Tenant's Request)</b><br /><br />\rShould the tenant wish to leave their contract early, they shall be liable to the\rlandlord's costs in re-letting the property as well as all rent due under the tenancy\runtil the start date of the replacement tenancy. These costs will be no more than the\rmaximum amount of rent outstanding on the tenancy.<br /><br />\r<b>Please ask a member of staff if you have any questions about our fees</b><br /><br />\r\r<b>Client Money Protection:</b> <u>.propertymark.co.uk</u> <br />\r\r<b>Independent Redress:</b> <u>.tpos.co.uk</u>",
